        "other_details": {
          "en": {
            "provenance": "translation_service",
            "value": "The country is in a serious state. Due to the lack of capable leadership, there is an urgent need to improve our nation, which is rich in beautiful, peaceful natural resources, and to prioritize the security of the country and its people through policy. To improve the political situation, if the state invests in education, health, and the environment, the country will make significant progress. Due to the closure of nationally owned factories, youth unemployment has risen, and the trend of going abroad must be immediately halted."
          },
          "ne": {
            "provenance": "imported",
            "value": "देशको गम्भिर अवस्था छ। कुशल नेतृत्व दिन नसकेकोले सुनदर शान्त प्राकृतिक श्रोतको भण्डारले भरिपूर्ण हाम्रो देशलाई सुधार गरी नितिगत रुपमा देश र जनताको सुरक्षाको प्राथमिक्ताको अवश्यकता छ। देशको राजनीतिक अवस्थामा सुधार गर्न शिक्षा स्वास्थ्य र पर्यावरणमा राज्यको लगाती भएमा देशले फड्को मार्ने छ। देशको राष्ट्रिय स्वामित्वका कल कारखाना वन्द भएकोले यूवा बेरोजगार बढेको कारण विदेशिने क्रमलाई तत्काल रोक्नु पर्छ।"
          }
        },
